data.description: Looking for a piece of land, with a move -in-ready condition home,work garage that is heated with water, near the park, for a piece of mind? ...Did we mention a double lot as well? This home is a super cozy home, nestled into the park, a 1-2 min walk to the boat launch and boat rental cabin of Lake Glacier. Location,location,location, yet amenities ,amenities, amenities seem more like it!
